cs.NI, cs.IT, cs.SY, cs.AI, cs.RO 

This paper deals with the optimization of UAV-assisted communication networks, which involves the design of trajectories and power allocation for the UAVs. This topic is closely related to network optimization (cs.NI), information theory (cs.IT), control systems (cs.SY), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and robotics (cs.RO). Therefore, these are the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper.
